text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to make peaches and cream cupcakes?
text.Response A:
Making the frosting


Beat icing sugar and butter together in a bowl until the mixture comes together.
text.Response B:
Add two ovals.

Draw a small oval at the right of the image.

Add two more legs.

Add the final leg by drawing three rectangles.
